New Product Alert 🚨 
We’ve built the best flip-flops, wallets, bags, shirts, shorts, rashguards, hats, and belts in the world.

Why not slides too?

That question became a mission—sparked by a request from one of our most well-known customers: President Donald J. Trump, who owns two pairs of Toeholds and asked us for a slide version. We didn’t hesitate.

Today, the first-ever Toehold Slides are officially live.
Handmade in America with full-grain leather, Vibram® outsoles, and zero toe post. Just raw comfort, toughness, and style—built the Toehold way.

What to expect:
• Full-grain American leather
• Water-resistant, contoured footbed
• Vibram® traction outsoles
• Handmade in the USA

Our longtime customers already know the benefits of being a Generation One owner.
If you don’t… you’ll have to learn firsthand.

This is a limited release, order today!
Slide in now.

Toehold, for every occasion.
